task.summary: Added gradle and changed the whole project to a gradle project
Fixes for showing pictures at initialize, need to fix dialogs they dont work
fixes on dialogs now they are showing up. also some changes to libs. no warnings now
added application path and a controller setter for easier controller access through the app

added a button for showing the location of the photos on a map it will show work if the photo has no GPS data
Also fixed a bug with the default selected album on the add to album method

Fixed issue with date from extracting metadata with some dirty code
Now you can change the database Date from varchar to Date but remeber to whipe the table first. We can now start making queries with order by date.
Fixes a problem with photos with no date tags and with photos with no metadata
Photo Model is changed to how mr petalidis asked
creating a new fxml for showing dates
Creating album from two specific dates is now implemented. Needs some bug fixing and error fixing but it works.
Changing the way things look and will now try to implement albums showing and staff
Added a view of the albums and a method for getting photos of a specific album
